channel.title: Um yea :\
channel.description: Ok i got 2 questions. #1 Every time i try to use moparscape the page comes up but it wont load. Instead on having the java icon at the top left it comes up with an X. Whats wrong? #2 When i go to Megaupload to download somthing or look for somthing ( like I tried to do with testscape) the page loaded but nothing came up..it had ads and everything. but no links for the site. whats wrong there?

item.title: Um yea :\
item.dc:creator: @billygotshot billygotshot
item.description:
@billygotshot wrote:

For question one you either have the wrong java or you dont have java at all… As for the second one if you use megaupload in the upper right hand side you will see some letters then a box next to it… Enter the letters you see into the box next to it then click download and wait 45 seconds then click the “click here to download” button. As for rapid share you need to scroll down and click on free then wait and click download and or enter some letters into a box like on megaupload.
